# Raster accuracy harness script
# Drives the freeze/analyse state machine through all 4 states and lets the
# trace report the mismatch count (the cart watch()es "mismatches" + "state"
# under DE_TRACE). Each SPACE/Z/X press re-enters analyse; the count for that
# state lands on the NEXT frame (SETUP→ANALYSE), so read frames 3/7/11/15.
#
# Run with:
#   node tools/play.js raster_test script tools/raster_test.script \
#        --headless --trace build/raster_trace.jsonl --frames 18
#   grep mismatches build/raster_trace.jsonl   # every state should report 0
#
# frame 2  SPACE → analyse  → f3  count: solid + outline   (out=1 dith=0)
# frame 6  Z (outline off)  → f7  count: solid, no outline  (out=0 dith=0)
# frame 10 X (dither on)    → f11 count: dither, no outline (out=0 dith=1)
# frame 14 Z (outline on)   → f15 count: dither + outline   (out=1 dith=1)

tap  2  SPACE
tap  6  Z
tap 10  X
tap 14  Z
